### Gelişmiş Animasyon Gereksinimleri

#### Sayfa Geçişleri
- **Page Transitions:** Framer Motion ile morphing transitions
- **Route Animations:** Slide, fade, scale kombinasyonları
- **Loading States:** Skeleton loading with shimmer effect
- **Progress Indicators:** Circular progress bars

#### Scroll Animasyonları
- **Parallax Scrolling:** Background, text, ve image parallax
- **Sticky Elements:** Header, navigation sticky behavior
- **Scroll-triggered Animations:** GSAP ScrollTrigger
- **Infinite Scroll:** Smooth infinite loading
- **Scroll Progress Bar:** Top progress indicator

#### Hover ve Interactive Efektleri
- **Magnetic Buttons:** Mouse takip eden butonlar
- **Tilt Effects:** 3D tilt on hover
- **Glow Effects:** Neon glow animations
- **Ripple Effects:** Material design ripple
- **Text Animations:** Letter by letter reveal
- **Image Zoom:** Smooth zoom on hover
- **Card Flip:** 3D card flip animations

#### Micro-interactions
- **Button States:** Loading, success, error states
- **Form Animations:** Input focus, validation animations
- **Notification Toasts:** Slide-in notifications
- **Tooltip Animations:** Smooth tooltip reveals
- **Menu Animations:** Hamburger menu morphing
- **Search Bar:** Expand/collapse with icon morphing

#### Advanced Animations
- **Lottie Animations:** Custom Lottie files for loading
- **Particle Effects:** Background particle systems
- **Wave Animations:** SVG wave effects
- **Morphing Shapes:** Shape-shifting elements
- **Text Typing:** Typewriter effect
- **Count-up Animations:** Number counting effects

